---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import MetricCard from "../../../components/MetricCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>

<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

<header class="mb-14">

<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
Electronic Invoicing SaaS
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
Unified invoicing system consolidating billing from multiple
products and integrating electronic invoicing regulations across
different countries.
</p>

</header>


<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">

<MetricCard value="+5000" label="invoices per day" />
<MetricCard value="3" label="billing domains unified" />
<MetricCard value="6" label="regulatory integrations" />

</div>


<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
The invoicing module consolidates billing from three independent
products: hotel PMS, activity management software and internal
management tools.
</p>

<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
The architecture was designed to support multiple regulatory
integrations, allowing new countries or administrations to be
added without affecting the core billing domain.
</p>

</article>

</BaseLayout>